imdb.plot outline: After the executive of a tourism company is accused of embezzlement & stealing the love of his life's project, he fake his own death. He transforms into Eva, a female assistant, to find evidence of who framed him and to be near the woman he loves.
imdb.title: Por ella soy Eva
